page.title: 05WEST COKER AREA LIFE STYLES
page.content: {THE ROYAL GEORGE. I LIVE AT THE ROYAL GEORGE,WEST COKER WHICH IS OWNED BY MY MUM AND DAD.MY PUB IS ABOUT THREE HUNDRED YEARS OLD.IT IS ONE OF THE OLDEST BUILDINGS IN THE VILLAGE.THERE ARE MANY OLD BUILDINGS IN WEST COKER INCLUDING THE ROYAL GEORGE.I LIKE LIVING IN A PUB,YOU GET TO KNOW LOTS OF PEOPLE. MY PUB IS NOT VERY BIG BUT IT IS AMAZING HOW MANY PEOPLE YOU CAN GET IN TO IT.AT CRISTMAS WE GET LOTS OF PEOPLE IN ESPECIALLY WHEN WE ALL HAVE FANCY DRESS.WE DO FOOD AS WELL AS DRINKS.WE HAVE FREEZER BAGS AND PUT THE FOOD TICKETS IN THEM SO THAT WE CAN TELL HOW MUCH WE HAVE SOLD. OUR PUB HAS A DARTS AND SKITTLES TEAM. NINE PEOPLE WORK IN MY PUB,SERVING BEHIND THE BAR,DOING MEALS OR CLEANING.
